          <p class='first-para'>
            I have listened closely to the remarks of the noble Baroness. I can only plead the obvious point in defence that she may not be entirely happy with the drafting, but the effect is to go as wide as possible&#x2014;wider than the individual elector. If the person came in with serious and proper intent, the obligation would be to provide that information. If we are erring, the error is in being as open and accountable as possible. I shall just have to accept the fact that the noble Baroness is not entirely happy with the drafting.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0658P0-02245'>
