            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_126gc' title='Col. 126GC &mdash; HL Deb 25 February 2004 vol 658 c126GC' name='column_126gc' href='#column_126gc' rel='bookmark'>126GC</a>
            offence is created, as I pointed out on Monday, but it means that the same sort of conduct will be criminal in both jurisdictions.
          </p>
