      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02429'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_231' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        On Question, amendment agreed to
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02430'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_232' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
