        <q>Page 37, line 30, leave out subsection (2).</q>
        <q>Page 37, line 35, leave out "the Secretary of State or</q>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02431'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_233' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
