      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0658P0-02460'>
        <a name='S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_262'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-bryan-davies' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_262' title='Link to this speech by Mr Bryan Davies' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-bryan-davies" title="Mr Bryan Davies">Lord Davies of Oldham</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I imagine that such sentiments can be expressed only from the Opposition Benches but I rise, too.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0658P0-02461'>
        <a name='S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_263'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-shelia-masters' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_263' title='Link to this speech by Ms Shelia Masters' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-shelia-masters" title="Ms Shelia Masters">Baroness Noakes</a></cite>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I beg leave to withdraw the amendment.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02462'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_264' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Amendment, by leave, withdrawn.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02463'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_265' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 67 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02464'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_266' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 68 [<span class="italic">Welsh NHS bodies</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02465'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_267' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        [<span class="italic">Amendment No. 62 not moved.</span>]
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02466'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_268' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 68 agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02467'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_269' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Remaining clauses and schedule agreed to.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02468'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_270' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Bill reported with amendments.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0658P0-02469'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0658P0_20040225_GCR_271' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        The Committee adjourned at half past five o'clock.
      </p>
